    public interface SqmNavigableReference
extends SqmExpression, NavigableReferenceInfo, SqmFromExporter, SemanticPathPart
    Represents a specific reference to a given Navigable in relation to an SQM query. E.g., a query defined as select .. from Person p1, Person p2 contains 2 different Navigable references: the SqmRoot references p1 and p2. So it is the same Navigable (Person entity), but 2 different NavigableReferences.

    Such a reference is a specialization of SqmExpression, meaning it can occur in any place in the query that an expression is valid - although some limitations do apply to specific contexts
